heading: Nostrava Deepwood Dungeon Guide
content: Nostrava Deepwood is a fast dungeon with the somewhat useless . Should you get a Nightmare Dungeon Sigil, consider this dungeon for fast completion times, especially due to the lack of an end of dungeon boss. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
